column17:
The following post uses a distract tactic by shifting the focus away from domestic political issues to international politics:

@SenWarren @POTUS U have had 2 years to do that maybe stop the proxy war in Ukraine and help the people in America

This tweet is discussing the proxy war in Ukraine, which is unrelated to the domestic political issues being addressed in the other posts. By bringing up an irrelevant topic, the user is attempting to distract from the main conversation about domestic politics.
